For those who are confused about why your audio keeps cutting out.  It is a sophisticated audio coding being integrated into the digital sound on the movie.  If you have a newer DVD/Blueray player or a PS3, your device will look for a "watermark" signal and if your chosen form of media does not also have this "watermark" it will cut your audio out.  Simple explanation.
